{"tid":137204,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 跪地求救 ]唔見咗2隻公仔，有無人可以話我知應該點做 (2.5)","createTime":"2017-02-27T15:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T17:33:41.000Z","uid":54324,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"976fb12fe9a37e820131cfb2a3c2524eacca0af5","tid":137204,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"(2)開錯台自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事源:<br />\n<br />\n星期一(20/02)13:30左右荃新天地往佐敦紅van漏低咗佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2czy7ofg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2czy7ofg&h=4c47e7ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用個藍色袋裝住<br />\n<br />\n玩公仔嘅人就會明佢地唔單單係公仔咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n司機話收車唔見有<br />\n點先可以搵得返佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿相認<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jky5r1l6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjky5r1l6&h=c3e43361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pgwbjuha\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpgwbjuha&h=610265e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已係荃灣同佐敦站頭+街頭貼街招<br />\n有酬 有消息請 tg: Topaazt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一個post傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/131771/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/131771/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係啊我仲未放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌我on9請細力啲<br />\n願天下公仔同主人永不分離<br />\n<br />\n27/2 23:36更新 補貼咗佐敦，司機未有影<br />\n<br />\n推到一家團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d49feec392f1ba8b6a0469