Z","msg":"(不是搵返)<br />\n有網友又寄了一對比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菩薩心腸嘅大家會好心有好報<br />\n利申 不是放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/odz41rls\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fodz41rls&h=e67a47dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1217a7c3520d2d5d677bc34f4018464e4794430b","tid":137204,"uid":87711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T20:37:50.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1113ddccec49879436094d13f4e3860142c8cd","tid":137204,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T21:11:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad0ece7f7009b9e2a7198c0ec07ce18d7c3ca783","tid":137204,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T21:14:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思想係度問少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲去過magic lab整公仔?我隻公仔d棉鬆晒想搵佢地整返好<br />\n宜家香港係咪得返呢間整公仔?<br />\n唔好意思off topic, 希望樓主快d搵返個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfcca2f503c02c11aad2e70f62395dc2287ddaa","tid":137204,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be19e90e35f7244015ab53e7cefda6d2da1f40d0","tid":137204,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思想係度問少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲去過magic lab整公仔?我隻公仔d棉鬆晒想搵佢地整返好<br />\n宜家香港係咪得返呢間整公仔?<br />\n唔好意思off topic, 希望樓主快d搵返個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無喎 不過聽聞整完會有一刻好肥 不過你試完可以上黎post下"},{"pid":"52041782de119c8e63b6282cf68222a9987b39c7","tid":137204,"uid":87577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"睇來樓主好似已經平復心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有埋同款公仔填返<br />\n會慢慢將舊的靈魂投射落佢地<br />\n好快會淡忘呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca4aa339bbc8051fb5da38c6c3d2dce108e52b6","tid":137204,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好意思想係度問少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲去過magic lab整公仔?我隻公仔d棉鬆晒想搵佢地整返好<br />\n宜家香港係咪得返呢間整公仔?<br />\n唔好意思off topic, 希望樓主快d搵返個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無喎 不過聽聞整完會有一刻好肥 不過你試完可以上黎post下</blockquote><br />\n我會要求佢唔好整咁脹<br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41da4c738dfbbee170d643b8f8d2b529c309cf48","tid":137204,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇來樓主好似已經平復心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有埋同款公仔填返<br />\n會慢慢將舊的靈魂投射落佢地<br />\n好快會淡忘呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的確係無咁傷心<br />\n但半夜都會諗起佢地<br />\n會繼續試下搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0f285e40c4d365876400933ee3d272fc7cc2f5","tid":137204,"uid":21965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇來樓主好似已經平復心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有埋同款公仔填返<br />\n會慢慢將舊的靈魂投射落佢地<br />\n好快會淡忘呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的確係無咁傷心<br />\n但半夜都會諗起佢地<br />\n會繼續試下搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望最後都可以同佢地團聚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f240892baa8f9e3be8b8d9f6ff354457ac88c39","tid":137204,"uid":5061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到你d街招   但幫唔到你手  唯有幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"f5113d91b62b7c3caa5b6b7179f33cd3f99685d8","tid":137204,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"搵到不如比對我<br />\n好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼哂車站應該搵得番既"},{"pid":"fd51e7b385b3107d90f739ffb4bb37f637be136c","tid":137204,"uid":53018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"已完？"},{"pid":"f7b641ec737938962d26238270d2afe567437e1e","tid":137204,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已完？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n消息的司機"},{"pid":"2fac420b783b2be345df95f2fe4a9647711f7be5","tid":137204,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已完？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n消<span style=\"color: red;\">失</span>的司機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c6b84abadb999d62fc13519d57391b4604fa0c","tid":137204,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:43:20.000Z","msg":"收到幾多對全新既公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係邊到買架？無追晒post點解咁珍而重之？<br />\n同埋你點分到個兩樣就係你仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff31bbf1cb74b2c034444be7bd0015c3c80c69b","tid":137204,"uid":87577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已完？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n消息的司機</blockquote><br />\n今日再去搵下啦"},{"pid":"b23659bb1b701d195ad7e83fe7318ea4c9d6a036","tid":137204,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"節哀順變啦 樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrip狗仔x2"},{"pid":"d79037427a0b2662e5274edd82240168baeda88a","tid":137204,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到幾多對全新既公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係邊到買架？無追晒post點解咁珍而重之？<br />\n同埋你點分到個兩樣就係你仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2對<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網友送贈個對好暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本<br />\n無乜故事, 但我會覺得佢地每隻都有自己性格<br />\n會扮佢地傾計(屌我痴線請細力啲)同埋同佢地玩<br />\n因為佢地有啲位係有疤<br />\n同埋黑色個隻個頭啲綿好鬆(我成日話佢無腦 要另一隻幫佢暖住個頭)<br />\n久而久之你日日望佢地會認得個感覺同眼神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf7c55553ffb0b2a0db77684e1725d6cf66ebe2","tid":137204,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b6a1e85c9251349861e22763487d245c53b29a","tid":137204,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收到幾多對全新既公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係邊到買架？無追晒post點解咁珍而重之？<br />\n同埋你點分到個兩樣就係你仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2對<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網友送贈個對好暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本<br />\n無乜故事, 但我會覺得佢地每隻都有自己性格<br />\n會扮佢地傾計(屌我痴線請細力啲)同埋同佢地玩<br />\n因為佢地有啲位係有疤<br />\n同埋黑色個隻個頭啲綿好鬆(我成日話佢無腦 要另一隻幫佢暖住個頭)<br />\n久而久之你日日望佢地會認得個感覺同眼神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算一樣都唔會代替到之前嗰隻<br />\n我都有隻摯愛喺屋企 陪左我十幾年<br />\n成日都會同佢講野 買埋條毛巾仔比佢當被冚<br />\n雖然好細隻（掌心細少少）方便攜帶<br />\n但我永遠都唔會帶佢出街<br />\n驚我一個唔小心跌左或者唔見左<br />\n因為就算搵到其他一樣嘅公仔都好（但我從來未見過出面有同我嗰隻一樣嘅）<br />\n但每當我返到屋企上床見到隻代替品<br />\n我就好自然會諗起<br />\n一個曾經陪我經歷左咁多野嘅'屋企人'<br />\n一個當我係佢生命嘅全部嘅屋企人<br />\n佢喺唔知咩人手上/甚至可能已經比人當垃圾掉左<br />\n佢一個'人'孤令令比人埋喺堆田區<br />\n一個又臭又凍嘅堆田區<br />\n永遠永遠...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}